question_details.resolution_criteria:
The question will be resolved as **Yes** if, at any time before January 1, 2026, one or both of the following conditions are met:

 • (1) Both the Associated Press and The New York Times report that the People's Republic of China has launched a full-scale invasion of Taiwan;

 • (2) At least 1,000 People's Liberation Army troops have been deployed in Taiwan with the aim of bringing the sovereignty of the main island under PRC control.
